column2: SELECT a.ra, a.dec, a.z, a.z_Err, a.logMass, a.logMass_err, a.t_age_mean, a.t_age_err, a.metallicity_mean, a.metallicity_err,    a.dust1_mean, a.dust1_err, a.tau_mean, a.tau_err, a.age_mean, a.age_min, a.age_max, a.ssfr_mean, a.ssfr_min, a.ssfr_max,   p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_z into mydb.MyTable from stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as a JOIN specobjall as s ON s.specObjID = a.specObjID JOIN photoobjall as p ON p.objID = s.bestobjID
